The Pincers are a group of islands located within the Wushanko Isles.

The following characters are known to be from this region:

  • Shura, a siren who is specifically from the island of Ashihama
  • The Nightmare, an otherworldy horror who feeds on the life force of sleeping people is from Ashihama
  • Ak-Haranu, a merchant in Port Phasmatys
  • San Fan, a representative of the Cutthroat in the Trouble Brewing minigame
  • Shanomi, a battle mage in charge of the animated armour in the Warriors' Guild
  • Necrovarus, a ghostly priest and mage who resides in Port Phasmatys
